Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:16.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}仿佛一望无际
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:23.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲伤已烟消云散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:30.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}为了不让这份笑容黯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:38.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}我会一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}没有泪水的明天过后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}会有温柔的未来等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:53.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}即便是微弱的希望 也相信着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:57.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life一定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 只属于自己的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:05.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}迷茫的时候携手前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}在现实(现在)中Survive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:11.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life会和你一同发现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:20.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}生而为人的证明 与促成邂逅的点滴
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.36,0:21:06.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}(Stay with you forever…)
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.08,0:21:16.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも続くような
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.33,0:21:23.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}悲しみはどこにもない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.38,0:21:30.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}その笑顔 曇らないように
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.22,0:21:38.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}いつでもそばにいるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.06,0:21:42.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}涙のない明日の先に
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.36,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}優しい未来はある
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.36,0:21:53.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}淡い 希望でも 信じよう
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.45,0:21:57.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of lifeきっと見つけられる
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Feel you heart 自分だけの答え
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.63,0:22:05.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}迷うときは 手を取り合って
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.30,0:22:07.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}現実(いま)をsurvive
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.84,0:22:11.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}Reason of life君と見つけられる
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.47,0:22:20.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}生まれてきた証に 出会う為の絆を
